<br>
We are an EQoA board. We are specifically designed to be a resource for the Wizard class. We enjoy discussing *almost* everything regarding EQoA, however, and in fact - can be found discussing EQ2, EQ1 and D&amp;D from time to time. No harm, no foul. Really OT stuff like the &quot;Bucs&quot; thread is cool too - because a message board community tends to gather for one purpose, and chat about other things too. So feel free to include your own OT posts in the General Discussion forum, but please - Use the common (OT) Subject format to let everyone know that your post is OFF TOPIC.<br>
<br>
2. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Harvesting our members</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
When done casually - &quot;Hey! Heres a link to teh Warriors of EQoA boards! Check it out if ya'r into it!&quot; I don't have a problem with it. SPAM advertising sucks though, so we need to actively discourage visitors with NO interest in US, from harvesting our members - especially if they use deciet to get traffic. To that end, we WILL *BAN* you if you deceptively post links to your site / board and your board is REALLY about monkey pr0n, cb radios, or womens volleyball. We may at our discretion retain a bookmark to your womens volleyball page, if you have a lot of good pictures, or something though! We will also BAN you if you post links to sites engaged in illegal behavior, such as buying / selling characters, items, Tunar, etc.<br>
<br>
3. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>P0rn</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
Welp, I love P0rn. Sometimes. Some kinds.  Good stuff, where appropriate. This is NOT that place, obviously. Why? Because we have no way to reliably verify AGE, for one thing. Oh, and we are a board dedicated to Wizards and EverQuest and EQoA, NOT p0rn. Duh. A good rule of thumb is: If you are in doubt about whether something is appropriate for this board, email me! If your really in doubt, it's probably NOT appropriate!<br>
<br>
4. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Multiposting / Threadbombing</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
Simultaneously posting the same thing to two or more areas of the board. That should be a no no, but not necessarily an insta-ban. It's just bad form. Don't do it! If you do it too much, you will get a warning, then a vacation, then a BAN. Kapeesh?<br>
<br>
5. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Disagreeing with ME</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
Or any of the satff here at WoE, is encouraged. Bear in mind that we doin't get paid, we have families, lives, and jobs. We like to play too! And so on. Use the appropriate channels. Like EMAIL. Mine is Ozzymandos@yahoo.com Dont keep posting the same @#%$ over and over everytime / anytime we lock something or move it to another forum. Email me. Or pick a fight with me in RANTS. Or just act like a grown up, even if your NOT.<br>
<br>
6. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Have FUN!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
If I have to explain this one to you, you need to log off for a while and go outside. Get some fresh air and stuff. You have been locked in your closet too long and frankly - you look kinda pale. Seek help!<br>
